FT  12 MAY 94 / Observer: Baby choirs
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
BhS, the retail store chain, either cares naught for product placement or
has never heard of Britain's biggest union.
The public services union, Unison - which has 1.5m members - is celebrating
